{"tid":2215224,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"戰機軍費 消耗戰恐累跨台灣","createTime":"2020-09-24T00:15:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-24T02:05:51.000Z","uid":118226,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"457f33249a7c65bfd13314ad9fc513c6401844d6","tid":2215224,"uid":118226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T00:15:03.000Z","msg":"面對解放軍軍機近期頻繁於台海進行實戰化訓練，台軍亦加緊升空應對。近日有台軍退役將領指出，緊急升空應對令台軍疲於奔命，造成<br />\n自2016年大陸軍機、軍艦赴台外圍海空域次數增加，台軍後勤成本持續攀升。台軍2017年後勤及通資業務費為659多億（約178億港元），隨後還動用5.9億多元（約1.6億港元）預備金支付缺額。其後由2018年至2020年，相關經費預算按年遞增。到2021年，今年更增至770多億元（約208億港元）。<br />\n<br />\n會上有軍事學者認為，戰機升空一趟燃料費便要花80萬至100萬元（約22萬至27萬港元），建議未來面對解放軍軍機擾台，可先用雷達鎖定，發現來者不善，再升空驅離。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20200923/bkn-20200923113525068-0923_00952_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20200923%2Fbkn-20200923113525068-0923_00952_001.html&d=NOH35fHRfA96o6n45SGJFP8K46P7%2BXxs1F7ZCKkfkQw%3D&h=c1d4061d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20200923/bkn-20200923113525068-0923_00952_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n台灣經濟唔夠撼 <br />\n侵侵快啲幫拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8040acca3799332ee95ec47583b003b4f911a4d","tid":2215224,"uid":254383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T00:23:44.000Z","msg":"R經費<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c5ac179eb569610c25fe271ffaaf6d36bbf4a37","tid":2215224,"uid":25424,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T00:26:08.000Z","msg":"中国D短命飛機飛就唔消耗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ede0431a5944f8bbae503cbc1bd7ae2b2c0c2898","tid":2215224,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c5ac179eb569610c25fe271ffaaf6d36bbf4a37","tid":22152